### Vixen API Test Requests
### Use with the REST Client extension

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: {{contentType}}

###

### Root endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Accept: {{contentType}}

###

### API Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/status
Accept: {{contentType}}

###

### Get Captcha (if implemented)
# GET {{baseUrl}}/api/captcha
# Accept: image/webp

###

### Test with invalid endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/invalid
Accept: {{contentType}}

###
